<br>
I was wondering a few things - I am at lvl 50, making work of getting to lvl 51 as soon as possible. <br>
<br>
How do I go about advancing my AA skills? <br>
How do I enable getting exp in those instead of regular exp making me level, and how do I turn it off again ?<br>
<br>
And is it wise to do some AA-skills at this level or is it wiser to wait until a later level?<br>
<br>
And how about Research? <br>
I have it at skill 150 now - do you need Research after your lvl 49 pet-spells? <br>
Or is it a skill best left alone from now on since there is no real need for it anymore?<br>
<br>
And what about spell drops for the lvl's 51, 52,etc, to 59 (or even to 60)? <br>
Where do they drop, off of which critters - are these critters soloable or does one need a group... ?<br>
<br>
I know I ask a lot of questions, and I know there are lots of resources on the net giving me the information, but it's (imho) better to ask in a forum then it is reading the pages and trying to find the items off the mobs.<br>
<br>
Thanks for giving any and all answers - and if you think the answers should be given not in this forum but privately - please e-mail me at ziggie@loveable.com<br>
Thank you ever so much.<br>
<br>
